## Priority Tiers

### MVP (Quick Mode)
```
• Topic
• Primary keyword
• Word count
• Tone
```

### Standard Mode
```
MVP +
• Article type
• Target audience
• Internal links
• Author name
• CTA goal
```

### Expert Mode
```
Standard +
• Secondary keywords
• Competitor analysis
• E-E-A-T details
• Schema selection
• PAA questions
• External sources
```

---

## Smart Defaults

| If user provides... | AI assumes... |
|---------------------|---------------|
| Only keyword | Auto-detect intent, word count, related keywords |
| Website URL | Scrape brand voice, find internal link opportunities |
| Competitor URL | Analyze content, find gaps, suggest angles |
| Industry only | Suggest trending topics, common keywords |

